snippet.title: The Bibites: Digital Life
snippet.description:
The Bibites is an Ongoing project to create digital lifeforms. This means genetics, evolution, and natural selection!
Feel free to stick around if that kind of stuff is as interesting to you as it is to me!

Correct spellings can include Bibittes, Bibits, Bebite, Bebittes, and all kinds of weird variations. It's up to you 🤷
